{"tid":1273610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方稱民陣遊行高峰期有19萬人","createTime":"2019-07-01T14:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T14:39:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71f0191c7caa9b570915be94032e4d9896b81044","tid":1273610,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"民陣發起的七一遊行，大會表示有55萬人參與，警方則稱經原定的遊行路線，最高峰時有19萬人。<br />\n<br />\n遊行下午約3時在維園中央草坪起步，龍尾至晚上9時半左右達抵，改為位於中環遮打道的終點，整個遊行歷時約6個半小時結束。<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人岑子杰說，遊行延續了社會五大訴求，但政府只把暫緩修訂逃犯條例，當成撤回草案，市民不會收貨，民怨仍然很重。<br />\n<br />\n他希望政府不要再逃避，盡快回應市民訴求及聆聽民意。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a428f51bc35e0ff6b9e1c69e6ddee969ae842c1e","tid":1273610,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:32:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466075-20190701.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466075-20190701.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=887927bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466075-20190701.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9e225931\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466075-20190701.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1fae66574af05406c370c10394c1763d4f12083b","tid":1273610,"uid":79181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"文宣幫傳<br />\n提防散水 <br />\n人少先危險<br />\n唔好信擇日再戰<br />\n全力支援現場決定<br />\n發夢香港人盡快出去支援準備反包圍<br />\n發夢需要各種補給<br />\n發夢需要照明燈<br />\n一定要頂住 堅持住！<br />\n香港要改變！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不撤不散<br />\n<br />\n一定要捉住今次機會<br />\n絕對唔好再浪費<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"b5b5783b702ca3d7759bdfc92a73688018ad047a","tid":1273610,"uid":267801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0